    "faq": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"apotecha-faq\"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"apotecha-faq__list\"><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>How Quickly Will I Notice A Difference?</summary><p>Most customers notice softer, more manageable hair within 2-3 washes.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>Is It Suitable For My Hair Type?</summary><p>Our shampoo bar works for all hair types — straight, wavy, curly, and coily.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>How Do I Use A Shampoo Bar?</summary><p>Wet your hair, rub the bar between your hands to create a lather, then massage into your scalp and hair.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>How Long Does One Bar Last?</summary><p>One bar typically lasts 60-80 washes, equivalent to 2-3 bottles of liquid shampoo.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>Will It Work With Colour Treated Hair?</summary><p>Yes. Our sulfate-free formula is gentle on colour-treated hair.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>Do You Ship Internationally?</summary><p>Yes, we ship worldwide. Delivery times vary by region.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>Is Rice Protein Right For Everyone?</summary><p>Rice protein is suitable for most hair types. If you have specific allergies, please check the full ingredients list.</p></details><details class=\"apotecha-faq__item\" name=\"faq\"><summary>What If I Don't Love It?</summary><p>We offer a 30-day money back guarantee — no questions asked.</p></details></div></div>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 80
      }
    },
    "clean_ingredients": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"apotecha-ingredients\"><h2 class=\"apotecha-ingredients__tagline\"><em>Clean Hair. Fewer Ingredients.</em></h2><div class=\"apotecha-ingredients__grid\"><div class=\"apotecha-ingredients__item\"><svg class=\"apotecha-ingredients__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 37\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M15 2v33M15 8c-4 0-8-3-12-6M15 8c4 0 8-3 12-6M15 16c-5 0-10-3-13-6M15 16c5 0 10-3 13-6M15 24c-4 0-9-3-12-6M15 24c4 0 9-3 12-6\"/></svg><h3>Amino Acids</h3><p>Packed with rice bran hydrolysed protein for visibly stronger and more resilient hair.</p></div><div class=\"apotecha-ingredients__item\"><svg class=\"apotecha-ingredients__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 37\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M15 37V15M15 15C15 8 8 2 2 2c0 8 6 13 13 13zM15 15c0-7 7-13 13-13 0 8-6 13-13 13z\"/></svg><h3>Botanical Extracts</h3><p>Enriched with green tea, rosemary, and chamomile for a healthier scalp and hair condition.</p></div><div class=\"apotecha-ingredients__item\"><svg class=\"apotecha-ingredients__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 37\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"18\" r=\"13\"/><path d=\"M10 13l5 5-5 5M20 13l-5 5 5 5\"/></svg><h3>Zero Waste</h3><p>Zero plastic packaging — one bar replaces up to 3 bottles of liquid shampoo.</p></div></div></div>",
